Information was received about a person who was dealing and selling drugs around Delmas policing area. The information was brought before court and a search warrant was authorised. A disruptive operation was executed in the early hours of Thursday, 19 May, in Delmas.  The team proceeded to the identified address where the suspect was searched and the following drugs were found and seized for further investigation: • 21× rock Cocaine valued R9450
• 26× pinches of Heroine valued R6500
• 17 402 grams of dagga valued R696 080
• Cash to the amount of R33 016. 80 The suspect will appear before the Delmas Magistrate’s Court on Friday (today). The investigation continues. 